        {
            "title": "越秀交通去年純利倒退14.2% 擬派末期息每股0.13元按年減13.3%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">越秀交通(01052)公布，2024年度股東應佔盈利6.57億元(人民幣．下同)，按年跌14.2；擬派末期息每股0.13港元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">今次末期息按年減少13.3%；若計入已派的中期息每股0.12元，全年共派息0.25元，全年派息率相等於58.5%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14773893-%e8%b6%8a%e7%a7%80%e4%ba%a4%e9%80%9a%e5%8e%bb%e5%b9%b4%e7%b4%94%e5%88%a9%e5%80%92%e9%80%8014-2-%e6%93%ac%e6%b4%be%e6%9c%ab%e6%9c%9f%e6%81%af%e6%af%8f%e8%82%a10-13%e5%85%83%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e6%b8%9b13",
